dct_title_s: Automobile road from Salinas to Watsonville and Castroville
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; A.J.B.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper left.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways.
Indicates distances from Salinas and Watsonville.
Numbered 320 in lower right corner and 81 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
